[9.205, "o", "**Package Structure:**\r\n\r\n```\r\n.\r\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 cmd/server/\r\n\u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 main.go          (package main)\r\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 internal/\r\n\u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 api/\r\n\u2502   \u2502   \u251c\u2500\u2500 handler.go      (package api)\r\n\u2502   \u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 middleware.go   (package api)\r\n\u2502   \u2514\u2500\u2500 db/\r\n\u2502       \u2514\u2500\u2500 postgres.go     (package db)\r\n```\r\n\r\nA typical Go project with `cmd/` for entry points, `internal/` for private packages (api and db), following Go best practices.\r\n[success] tokens: 6388 in / 297 out\r\n"]
